ast.name: hawaii store
ast.comment:
A library that provide cloud-based key-value storage.
The library requires an account with Microsoft Research Project Hawaii Services. See demo for usage example.

app.name: hawaii path prediction
app.comment:
A library that provide path prediction based on a history of positions.
The library requires an account with Microsoft Research Project Hawaii Services. See demo for usage example.
Given a set of locations, predicts future path. Uses the Project Hawaii services from Microsoft Research.
